Since I brought it up today, I should make it today.

518
00:25:05,371 --> 00:25:06,400
I'll try it.

519
00:25:06,401 --> 00:25:07,471
It's good.

520
00:25:08,171 --> 00:25:09,771
He looks so happy.

521
00:25:10,971 --> 00:25:14,341
(Can he escape from getting 0 vote today?)

522
00:25:15,751 --> 00:25:18,081
(Trembling)

523
00:25:18,481 --> 00:25:22,351
(Did Ji Hye send Jin Wu her Love QR?)

524
00:25:23,091 --> 00:25:25,421
(Nervous)

525
00:25:26,421 --> 00:25:28,730
(You have received no Love QR message.)

526
00:25:28,731 --> 00:25:29,791
No message.

527
00:25:29,831 --> 00:25:32,230
(The MCs break down from too much pity.)

528
00:25:32,231 --> 00:25:33,400
There's really none?

529
00:25:33,401 --> 00:25:34,860
(The shock of the 0 vote is too strong.)

530
00:25:34,861 --> 00:25:36,500
I thought he wouldn't get one, but he really didn't?

531
00:25:36,501 --> 00:25:38,641
I don't get Ji Hye.

532
00:25:40,271 --> 00:25:42,371
I mean, when Jin Wu asked...

533
00:25:42,411 --> 00:25:44,370
if she'd go on a date with him again...

534
00:25:44,371 --> 00:25:46,510
if he chose her,

535
00:25:46,511 --> 00:25:47,681
Ji Hye said,

536
00:25:47,781 --> 00:25:48,980
"It'll be strange if you didn't."

537
00:25:48,981 --> 00:25:50,510
So why didn't she send him the QR?

538
00:25:50,511 --> 00:25:53,221
That was before the catfish arrived.

539
00:25:53,521 --> 00:25:54,881
She changed so fast?

540
00:25:55,421 --> 00:25:56,721
Love moves.

541
00:26:06,401 --> 00:26:08,501
(Deep sigh)

542
00:26:12,301 --> 00:26:16,141
I remember Ji Hye holding my hand teasingly,

543
00:26:16,911 --> 00:26:20,511
and I remember all the fun moments we had today.

544
00:26:22,051 --> 00:26:24,880
She went on two dates on the same day,

545
00:26:24,881 --> 00:26:28,251
and she picked the other guy over me.

546
00:26:28,991 --> 00:26:30,950
That means my date wasn't good enough.

547
00:26:30,951 --> 00:26:33,191
She did nothing wrong, of course.

548
00:26:33,991 --> 00:26:37,591
I should think about how to do better.

549
00:26:38,901 --> 00:26:41,700
(The last straw to their breakdown)

550
00:26:41,701 --> 00:26:43,030
Jin Wu.

551
00:26:43,031 --> 00:26:45,371
This is driving me mad.

552
00:26:48,271 --> 00:26:50,640
This is a lot more nerve-wracking than I thought.

553
00:26:50,641 --> 00:26:52,611
(Ji Hye sent her Love QR to Jeong Won.)

554
00:26:52,741 --> 00:26:54,310
(You have received one Love QR message.)

555
00:26:54,311 --> 00:26:57,981
(What Love QR did Ji Hye send to Jeong Won?)

556
00:26:58,111 --> 00:27:02,791
(The first Love QR)

557
00:27:03,091 --> 00:27:06,760
I took a photo of the sunset during the date...

558
00:27:06,761 --> 00:27:08,190
because it was pretty.

559
00:27:08,191 --> 00:27:09,331
I just sent that.

560
00:27:09,861 --> 00:27:13,001
It's pretty. Look at the sky.

561
00:27:13,101 --> 00:27:15,100
- The sky is pretty.
- It's pretty.

562
00:27:15,101 --> 00:27:18,171
(She took the sunset photo right next to Jeong Won.)

563
00:27:18,271 --> 00:27:19,470
"It's me."

564
00:27:19,471 --> 00:27:22,001
I made it obvious.

565
00:27:22,371 --> 00:27:23,741
It's so sweet.

566
00:27:25,541 --> 00:27:26,741
(Grinning)

567
00:27:27,411 --> 00:27:28,441
Actually,

568
00:27:29,811 --> 00:27:33,451
the date with Jin Wu was really fun,

569
00:27:34,051 --> 00:27:39,361
so I thought I'd stick to Jin Wu.

570
00:27:40,361 --> 00:27:42,991
but the date with Jeong Won...

571
00:27:43,261 --> 00:27:45,801
was more fun.

572
00:27:47,401 --> 00:27:51,201
(Ji Hye and Jeong Won chose each other.)

573
00:27:51,531 --> 00:27:55,611
(The second night is full of tangled emotions.)

574
00:27:57,671 --> 00:27:59,341
Ji Hye.

575
00:27:59,881 --> 00:28:01,380
- Can I have a minute?
- Yes?

576
00:28:01,381 --> 00:28:02,611
(Jin Wu goes to Ji Hye right after the Love QR session ends.)

577
00:28:02,881 --> 00:28:04,751
- Are you cold?
- No, I'm fine.

578
00:28:04,851 --> 00:28:06,021
Do you want to talk inside?

579
00:28:06,421 --> 00:28:07,551
Okay.

580
00:28:08,521 --> 00:28:09,750
(Jin Wu invites Ji Hye to a talk.)

581
00:28:09,751 --> 00:28:12,360
Jin Wu is a man.

582
00:28:12,361 --> 00:28:13,521
(Jin Wu invites Ji Hye to a talk.)

583
00:28:14,621 --> 00:28:16,030
You must be tired,

584
00:28:16,031 --> 00:28:17,390
so I'll make this quick.

585
00:28:17,391 --> 00:28:18,491
Okay.

586
00:28:18,861 --> 00:28:20,160
You make it sound so scary.

587
00:28:20,161 --> 00:28:21,601
Not at all.

588
00:28:22,231 --> 00:28:23,901
- Are you scared?
- No.

589
00:28:24,531 --> 00:28:26,470
I want to apologize to you.

590
00:28:26,471 --> 00:28:28,070
- Yes.
- I...

591
00:28:28,071 --> 00:28:31,370
I said I'd make you spicy stir-fried pork.

592
00:28:31,371 --> 00:28:32,411
Yes.

593
00:28:32,541 --> 00:28:34,741
- I cooked it to keep my word.
- Yes.

594
00:28:35,511 --> 00:28:37,710
I didn't think it'd become so big. I swear.

595
00:28:37,711 --> 00:28:39,021
I thought...

596
00:28:39,851 --> 00:28:42,721
you might find the situation uncomfortable.

597
00:28:42,751 --> 00:28:43,820
No.

598
00:28:43,821 --> 00:28:45,691
I didn't feel uncomfortable.

599
00:28:47,061 --> 00:28:48,621
Actually,

600
00:28:50,161 --> 00:28:51,831
when I'm interested in someone,

601
00:28:52,331 --> 00:28:54,100
the only thing I know to do is to make it obvious.

602
00:28:54,101 --> 00:28:56,271
I don't know how to make it subtle.

603
00:28:56,771 --> 00:29:01,271
I show everything with my actions.

604
00:29:01,701 --> 00:29:04,010
I don't feel embarrassed to ask you for a chat...

605
00:29:04,011 --> 00:29:05,481
in front of others.

606
00:29:05,541 --> 00:29:07,811
But that might make you feel uncomfortable.

607
00:29:09,381 --> 00:29:11,411
Oh, dear.

608
00:29:11,951 --> 00:29:14,181
Why is this making my hands tremble?

609
00:29:14,521 --> 00:29:16,990
(How cute.)

610
00:29:16,991 --> 00:29:20,591
(Jin Wu becomes nervous to convey his true feelings.)

611
00:29:20,907 --> 00:29:23,077
You should do what you feel like.

612
00:29:24,131 --> 00:29:24,926
I...

613
00:29:26,961 --> 00:29:29,000
Honestly, I went on...

614
00:29:29,001 --> 00:29:32,441
the 1-on-1 date with you in the morning for the 1st time.

615
00:29:33,270 --> 00:29:36,070
I really had fun.

616
00:29:37,011 --> 00:29:40,911
Had Jeong Won not joined today,

617
00:29:42,651 --> 00:29:44,711
I would've chosen you.

618
00:29:45,411 --> 00:29:49,751
But after talking with Jeong Won today...

619
00:29:52,491 --> 00:29:53,520
(Nervous)

620
00:29:53,521 --> 00:29:54,561
Poor him.

621
00:29:56,031 --> 00:29:59,531
The feeling of ease I feel when I'm with you...

622
00:30:00,301 --> 00:30:03,801
and the feeling of ease I feel when I'm with him are different.

623
00:30:04,271 --> 00:30:05,641
They feel different.

624
00:30:06,371 --> 00:30:07,541
So...

625
00:30:07,841 --> 00:30:12,310
I was quite concerned about you just now...

626
00:30:12,311 --> 00:30:14,941
because during our date,

627
00:30:15,581 --> 00:30:17,410
we said stuff like,

628
00:30:17,411 --> 00:30:19,450
"I'll send you the Love QR today,"

629
00:30:19,451 --> 00:30:21,121
and "I'll get upset if you don't send me the Love QR."

630
00:30:22,021 --> 00:30:26,161
But my feelings somehow ended up changing today.

631
00:30:26,261 --> 00:30:27,520
Rather than change,

632
00:30:27,521 --> 00:30:30,531
I chose the person I had more fun with today.

633
00:30:31,531 --> 00:30:34,861
Ji Hye is trying her best not to hurt him.

634
00:30:36,501 --> 00:30:37,971
That's what it is.

635
00:30:38,331 --> 00:30:40,541
I'm sorry. I want to apologize too.

636
00:30:40,941 --> 00:30:43,911
- I want to apologize.
- I didn't come here...

637
00:30:44,341 --> 00:30:47,241
to find out why you didn't send me the QR or hear your apology.

638
00:30:47,881 --> 00:30:50,711
I wanted to know if I could continue to express my feelings...

639
00:30:50,911 --> 00:30:53,321
to the person I sent my Love QR to today.

640
00:30:53,681 --> 00:30:54,780
That's a lot more important to me.

641
00:30:54,781 --> 00:30:56,721
Who you sent your QR to today isn't important.

642
00:30:57,891 --> 00:30:59,120
If that's how you feel...

643
00:30:59,121 --> 00:31:00,920
Your choice is yours to make.

644
00:31:00,921 --> 00:31:02,221
So that doesn't bother me.

645
00:31:03,691 --> 00:31:06,161
But if me continuing to approach you...

646
00:31:07,201 --> 00:31:09,731
is a waste of time, makes you uncomfortable,

647
00:31:09,771 --> 00:31:11,531
or makes you feel bad,

648
00:31:12,341 --> 00:31:14,441
then I want to stop because I feel sorry.

649
00:31:15,001 --> 00:31:16,210
(Thinking)

650
00:31:16,211 --> 00:31:18,141
But it's only been two days.

651
00:31:18,841 --> 00:31:22,280
If I start to feel your feelings are making me uncomfortable,

652
00:31:22,281 --> 00:31:24,380
I'll tell you frankly.

653
00:31:24,381 --> 00:31:25,751
I think that's the right thing.

654
00:31:26,581 --> 00:31:28,781
Honestly, this is the second day,

655
00:31:28,881 --> 00:31:31,651
so I don't know how my feelings will change.

656
00:31:34,421 --> 00:31:36,360
I won't feel upset or anything...

657
00:31:36,361 --> 00:31:39,101
because you don't end up choosing me.

658
00:31:39,831 --> 00:31:42,371
You don't have to worry about that.

659
00:31:43,101 --> 00:31:44,131
- My gosh.
- Okay.

660
00:31:44,771 --> 00:31:46,471
Only you know how you feel.

661
00:31:50,741 --> 00:31:52,780
Thank you for saying that.

662
00:31:52,781 --> 00:31:54,610
(Ji Hye is grateful that Jin Wu understands her.)

663
00:31:54,611 --> 00:31:56,551
He's really a nice guy.

664
00:31:59,021 --> 00:32:00,181
Shall we go back?

665
00:32:00,881 --> 00:32:01,921
Yes.

666
00:32:03,651 --> 00:32:04,691
(Adjusting)

667
00:32:06,521 --> 00:32:08,691
Jin Wu is very charming.

668
00:32:10,061 --> 00:32:11,831
I'll go shed some tears in my room.

669
00:32:14,201 --> 00:32:15,871
You must shed a lot.

670
00:32:15,971 --> 00:32:16,971
- Got it?
- I'll bawl my eyes out.

671
00:32:16,972 --> 00:32:18,471
You must recognize me even if my eyes swell tomorrow.

672
00:32:18,571 --> 00:32:19,600
Okay.

673
00:32:19,601 --> 00:32:21,141
(He forces himself to crack a joke in case Ji Hye feels uncomfortable.)

674
00:32:23,041 --> 00:32:28,581
(But once he comes back alone, he can't help but sigh.)

675
00:32:30,851 --> 00:32:35,381
(He said goodnight cheerfully, but he doesn't feel that way.)

676
00:32:37,821 --> 00:32:39,220
That's so sad.

677
00:32:39,221 --> 00:32:40,961
Her feelings are her own.

678
00:32:43,091 --> 00:32:45,630
I can't control what others feel.

679
00:32:45,631 --> 00:32:47,231
So I'll do it my way.

680
00:32:48,931 --> 00:32:52,871
(Will Jin Wu continue to have feelings for Ji Hye?)

681
00:32:53,501 --> 00:32:54,871
Isn't he really nice?

682
00:32:55,141 --> 00:32:56,541
- My heart aches so much.
- Honestly,

683
00:32:57,011 --> 00:32:59,580
Jin Wu is the best typical younger boyfriend material.

684
00:32:59,581 --> 00:33:01,341
Yes, I totally agree.

685
00:33:01,611 --> 00:33:04,581
That's the side of himself which Jin Wu can show off.

686
00:33:05,011 --> 00:33:06,551
Honest and simple.

687
00:33:06,821 --> 00:33:09,821
When this happens, you can't erase him from your memory.

688
00:33:10,021 --> 00:33:11,490
- Right?
- He keeps lingering in your mind.

689
00:33:11,491 --> 00:33:12,491
Yes.

690
00:33:13,291 --> 00:33:16,060
(Meanwhile, Yun So, another younger man,)

691
00:33:16,061 --> 00:33:18,791
(looks for his older woman.)

692
00:33:20,161 --> 00:33:22,200
- My goodness.
- You're back.

693
00:33:22,201 --> 00:33:23,400
(Yun So finds Ju Hee, whom he was looking for.)

694
00:33:23,401 --> 00:33:24,431
I'm back.

695
00:33:24,971 --> 00:33:27,141
- Can we talk?
- Talk? Okay.

696
00:33:27,601 --> 00:33:29,670
Where are we going?

697
00:33:29,671 --> 00:33:31,111
We can go to my room.

698
00:33:31,471 --> 00:33:32,841
- Since it's cold out here.
- Okay.

699
00:33:35,411 --> 00:33:36,581
It feels awkward again.

700
00:33:37,281 --> 00:33:38,811
I wonder what Yun So will do.

701
00:33:40,481 --> 00:33:41,881
Did someone trigger your curiosity?

702
00:33:42,821 --> 00:33:46,390
(Yun So, who is feeling anxious, fails to stop himself.)

703
00:33:46,391 --> 00:33:49,091
He asked her even before they took off their shoes.

704
00:33:49,431 --> 00:33:51,061
He asked as he removed his shoes.

705
00:33:52,261 --> 00:33:54,031
Did someone trigger your curiosity?

706
00:33:55,331 --> 00:33:57,631
The one I said before.

707
00:33:57,971 --> 00:33:59,101
- Jun Han?
- Yes.

708
00:34:00,201 --> 00:34:01,601
If you're curious about someone...

709
00:34:02,071 --> 00:34:03,071
I...

710
00:34:03,072 --> 00:34:04,541
You should check him out.

711
00:34:05,511 --> 00:34:07,640
I just wanted to hear the truth...

712
00:34:07,641 --> 00:34:10,080
since we talked openly just now.

713
00:34:10,081 --> 00:34:12,111
"I already told him."

714
00:34:12,251 --> 00:34:14,150
"It should be fine, right?"

715
00:34:14,151 --> 00:34:15,950
(During the date)

716
00:34:15,951 --> 00:34:18,320
That's why I wanted to ask you...

717
00:34:18,321 --> 00:34:19,790
(Yun So wanted to hear Ju Hee's honest feelings.)

718
00:34:19,791 --> 00:34:20,961
As soon as I came back.

719
00:34:21,521 --> 00:34:24,261
If you spend time with him...

720
00:34:25,061 --> 00:34:27,461
and think he's better,

721
00:34:29,301 --> 00:34:30,431
it's fine.

722
00:34:30,631 --> 00:34:31,770
That's your choice to make.

723
00:34:31,771 --> 00:34:34,071
I can't tell you what to do.

724
00:34:35,201 --> 00:34:36,241
Okay.

725
00:34:40,911 --> 00:34:42,551
Don't mind me, really.

726
00:34:43,651 --> 00:34:44,811
- Really?
- Yes.

727
00:34:47,751 --> 00:34:49,221
But my feelings won't waver.

728
00:34:49,791 --> 00:34:52,251
That I'm sure of.

729
00:34:52,491 --> 00:34:53,920
So you can go and come back.

730
00:34:53,921 --> 00:34:54,990
Okay.

731
00:34:54,991 --> 00:34:56,191
"You can go and come back."

732
00:34:56,861 --> 00:34:58,190
(Yu Jin and Ji Seung's room)

733
00:34:58,191 --> 00:35:00,100
I'm going to talk with Jun Han.

734
00:35:00,101 --> 00:35:01,500
I really don't understand.

735
00:35:01,501 --> 00:35:02,700
- Jun Han?
- Yes.

736
00:35:02,701 --> 00:35:03,701
Why?

737
00:35:03,702 --> 00:35:05,471
Because he sent you the QR?

738
00:35:05,631 --> 00:35:06,840
He didn't.

739
00:35:06,876 --> 00:35:08,776
- Really?
- Today?

740
00:35:08,801 --> 00:35:10,340
Who did he send it to?

741
00:35:10,341 --> 00:35:12,110
I think he sent it to the catfish.

742
00:35:12,111 --> 00:35:14,740
- To her?
- He suddenly sent it to her?

743
00:35:14,741 --> 00:35:16,411
Exactly. They had a date.

744
00:35:17,051 --> 00:35:19,220
Right, he had a date with the catfish.

745
00:35:19,221 --> 00:35:20,420
- Right.
- He should send it to her...

746
00:35:20,421 --> 00:35:21,621
since they went on a date.

747
00:35:21,981 --> 00:35:23,098
He went on a date with me too.

748
00:35:24,091 --> 00:35:25,490
- Today.
- You're right.

749
00:35:25,491 --> 00:35:26,591
In the morning.

750
00:35:26,761 --> 00:35:28,490
This is shocking. I didn't expect this.

751
00:35:28,491 --> 00:35:29,690
Everyone does something unexpected.

752
00:35:29,691 --> 00:35:31,261
Exactly. I'm so curious.

753
00:35:31,731 --> 00:35:33,800
At first, he...

754
00:35:33,801 --> 00:35:36,530
I said I rather got to like him...

755
00:35:36,531 --> 00:35:38,731
- after we went on the date.
- Yes.

756
00:35:39,001 --> 00:35:40,070
He treated me so nicely,

757
00:35:40,071 --> 00:35:42,171
so I thought he must treat his girlfriend really well...

758
00:35:42,741 --> 00:35:44,871
and that he's very devoted.

759
00:35:45,211 --> 00:35:46,741
But after seeing the voting result,

760
00:35:47,341 --> 00:35:48,710
I'm starting to think,

761
00:35:48,711 --> 00:35:51,080
"Did he treat me nicely because he wanted my vote?"

762
00:35:51,081 --> 00:35:52,211
No way.

763
00:35:52,311 --> 00:35:53,450
She must be hurt.

764
00:35:53,451 --> 00:35:55,220
Maybe that's just how he is.

765
00:35:55,221 --> 00:35:56,491
- He's just...
- But...

766
00:35:56,591 --> 00:35:59,621
actually, how he acted...

767
00:36:00,421 --> 00:36:01,490
isn't something to be frowned upon.

768
00:36:01,491 --> 00:36:03,560
- Since he's in here, - Yes.

769
00:36:03,561 --> 00:36:05,931
he should act that way.

770
00:36:06,661 --> 00:36:07,700
This is so...

771
00:36:07,701 --> 00:36:09,770
I don't think he did that for the vote.

772
00:36:09,771 --> 00:36:11,501
- I don't think he's like that.
- No way.

773
00:36:11,571 --> 00:36:14,371
I don't think he's the cunning type.

774
00:36:16,641 --> 00:36:19,610
I don't know whom I should get to know more now.

775
00:36:19,611 --> 00:36:20,611
What do I do?

776
00:36:20,612 --> 00:36:22,680
Nobody knows how things will change.

777
00:36:22,681 --> 00:36:23,751
I agree.

778
00:36:24,151 --> 00:36:25,781
We still have six days left.

779
00:36:26,521 --> 00:36:28,421
Or just Si Won?

780
00:36:29,121 --> 00:36:30,591
Or just Si Won?

781
00:36:30,921 --> 00:36:32,550
(Surprised)

782
00:36:32,551 --> 00:36:35,361
I think our emotions will run parallel.

783
00:36:36,291 --> 00:36:37,861
(Glancing)

784
00:36:38,491 --> 00:36:39,961
Oh, dear. Okay.

785
00:36:40,601 --> 00:36:42,501
Because for me,

786
00:36:42,771 --> 00:36:45,601
I don't do well with a very outgoing person.

787
00:36:46,401 --> 00:36:49,171
I go well with someone calm.

788
00:36:49,711 --> 00:36:51,310
I think Si Won is...

789
00:36:51,311 --> 00:36:54,011
- very decisive.
- Yes.

790
00:36:54,341 --> 00:36:57,011
He seems to be well-grounded.

791
00:36:57,451 --> 00:37:00,621
(She seems to be a bit flustered at the sudden mention of Si Won.)

792
00:37:01,021 --> 00:37:02,950
But it's only been two days.

793
00:37:02,951 --> 00:37:05,121
(Where will the older women's hearts head to?)

794
00:37:05,821 --> 00:37:09,561
(Meanwhile, Jun Han runs to find someone.)

795
00:37:09,861 --> 00:37:11,631
Nobody is there.

796
00:37:11,991 --> 00:37:13,631
- Did everyone go back?
- Yes.

797
00:37:14,901 --> 00:37:16,001
We...

798
00:37:16,831 --> 00:37:17,900
What?

799
00:37:17,901 --> 00:37:19,471
(Jun Han runs into Ju Hee by chance.)

800
00:37:19,901 --> 00:37:21,171
You noticed.

801
00:37:21,771 --> 00:37:23,041
(Jun Han is flustered.)

802
00:37:23,211 --> 00:37:25,011
- I wasn't sure, but now I am.
- Really?

803
00:37:26,481 --> 00:37:27,511
Yes.

804
00:37:27,811 --> 00:37:28,941
- Are you cold?
- No.

805
00:37:29,281 --> 00:37:31,181
- You're not?
- I'm wearing an angora sweater.

806
00:37:31,781 --> 00:37:33,351
- Then shall we talk?
- Sure.

807
00:37:35,351 --> 00:37:38,390
(Jun Han asks for a chat with Ju Hee, who chose him.)

808
00:37:38,391 --> 00:37:40,691
- I've wanted to talk with you.
- Me too.

809
00:37:41,921 --> 00:37:42,991
Then...

810
00:37:45,061 --> 00:37:47,161
- We voted today.
- Yes.

811
00:37:47,861 --> 00:37:51,131
Did you not vote for Yun So...

812
00:37:51,471 --> 00:37:53,340
just because you wanted to talk with me?

813
00:37:53,341 --> 00:37:54,371
Yes.

814
00:37:56,241 --> 00:37:58,371
- I was curious too.
- Yes.

815
00:37:58,541 --> 00:38:01,580
We always sat next to each other,

816
00:38:01,581 --> 00:38:03,411
and we did talk a bit,

817
00:38:03,781 --> 00:38:07,950
but we never got to talk deeply, just the two of us.

818
00:38:07,951 --> 00:38:09,751
So I was curious.

819
00:38:10,021 --> 00:38:12,450
I wasn't sure if I could do that.

820
00:38:12,451 --> 00:38:14,261
- Why would you say that?
- I mean...

821
00:38:14,491 --> 00:38:16,491
You were talking with Yun So.

822
00:38:16,631 --> 00:38:19,461
I could see something going on, so just in case...

823
00:38:19,801 --> 00:38:21,301
Yes, he would feel unsure.

824
00:38:21,501 --> 00:38:24,231
I didn't want to get in between you two.

825
00:38:25,271 --> 00:38:26,971
So I just kept quiet.

826
00:38:27,541 --> 00:38:29,841
- We've only just started.
- Well...

827
00:38:31,811 --> 00:38:34,680
We've just started, but so many things have happened.

828
00:38:34,681 --> 00:38:37,111
Exactly. It's scary.

829
00:38:37,181 --> 00:38:38,651
- It's scary, right?
- Yes.

830
00:38:38,851 --> 00:38:40,821
To be very honest,

831
00:38:41,351 --> 00:38:43,191
it might not seem nice,

832
00:38:43,521 --> 00:38:45,321
but we're all strangers.

833
00:38:45,421 --> 00:38:47,761
Instead of a group setting,

834
00:38:47,861 --> 00:38:49,861
I want to talk with everyone...

835
00:38:50,461 --> 00:38:52,361
- in a 1-on-1 setting.
- Me too.

836
00:38:52,861 --> 00:38:55,701
I still want to get to know others too.

837
00:38:55,761 --> 00:38:56,800
- Really?
- Yes.

838
00:38:56,801 --> 00:38:58,831
- I think that's good.
- Yes.

839
00:38:59,401 --> 00:39:00,901
It's good to talk with everyone.

840
00:39:01,641 --> 00:39:03,511
Yes, that's the right thing to do.

841
00:39:05,111 --> 00:39:06,411
How was today's date?

842
00:39:06,611 --> 00:39:08,841
Today's date was...

843
00:39:09,711 --> 00:39:10,850
comfortable...

844
00:39:10,851 --> 00:39:14,650
(Comfortable)

845
00:39:14,651 --> 00:39:16,121
- And nice.
- Really?

846
00:39:16,821 --> 00:39:19,021
Do you think you'll date him tomorrow too?

847
00:39:19,991 --> 00:39:21,721
But I'd like to go on a date with you.

848
00:39:21,821 --> 00:39:22,891
- Really?
- Yes.

849
00:39:23,531 --> 00:39:26,261
(Ju Hee told him her honest feelings.)

850
00:39:26,461 --> 00:39:28,561
Thank you. I...

851
00:39:29,531 --> 00:39:30,771
can make you laugh.

852
00:39:31,571 --> 00:39:34,000
While you're on a date with me, I promise...

853
00:39:34,001 --> 00:39:35,341
to make you laugh at least once.

854
00:39:35,771 --> 00:39:36,771
I mean it.

855
00:39:38,763 --> 00:39:41,103
Yes. So...

856
00:39:42,241 --> 00:39:43,551
Well, I didn't know,

857
00:39:43,711 --> 00:39:46,180
but all of them apparently dropped the honorifics.

858
00:39:46,181 --> 00:39:47,951
It surprised me.

859
00:39:48,621 --> 00:39:51,120
I was worried it might become a habit...

860
00:39:51,121 --> 00:39:53,561
if I didn't drop the honorifics now.

861
00:39:55,361 --> 00:39:57,261
- Should we start now, then?
- Sure.

862
00:39:59,131 --> 00:40:02,101
Oh, my gosh. They're so lovey-dovey.

863
00:40:02,871 --> 00:40:04,001
It is a bit embarrassing, though.

864
00:40:05,571 --> 00:40:10,171
(While Jun Han and Ju Hee are getting closer...)

865
00:40:10,771 --> 00:40:12,071
I'm not sure.

866
00:40:14,411 --> 00:40:18,181
(Yun So seems to have a lot on his mind.)

867
00:40:21,281 --> 00:40:24,151
(Staring)

868
00:40:25,104 --> 00:40:26,204
She said she didn't have any sheet masks.

869
00:40:27,411 --> 00:40:28,261
I should bring her some.

870
00:40:29,091 --> 00:40:32,460
Let's see. Is this enough?

871
00:40:32,461 --> 00:40:33,461
(He picks up some sheet masks...)

872
00:40:33,462 --> 00:40:36,901
(and heads to Ju Hee's room.)

873
00:40:37,701 --> 00:40:39,170
(Knocking)

874
00:40:39,171 --> 00:40:40,171
No one's here?

875
00:40:40,920 --> 00:40:42,120
Anyone here?

876
00:40:43,011 --> 00:40:45,971
- No!
- She's not there!

877
00:40:46,554 --> 00:40:48,414
This is bad timing!

878
00:40:48,711 --> 00:40:50,151
Stay at home.

879
00:40:51,951 --> 00:40:53,051
I should come back.

880
00:40:53,351 --> 00:40:55,321
- Where is he going?
- Maybe she's in the Talk Room.

881
00:40:57,251 --> 00:40:58,790
(Shivering)

882
00:40:58,791 --> 00:41:00,761
No! Yun So, this is too...

883
00:41:01,661 --> 00:41:02,720
Who's in the Talk Room?

884
00:41:02,721 --> 00:41:03,730
(He walks toward the Talk Room.)

885
00:41:03,731 --> 00:41:05,161
- Not now!
- Is there someone inside?

886
00:41:05,861 --> 00:41:07,230
No way.

887
00:41:07,231 --> 00:41:08,343
(Please stop.)

888
00:41:08,492 --> 00:41:09,477
Who's in the Talk Room?

889
00:41:09,571 --> 00:41:10,571
(He walks toward the Talk Room.)

890
00:41:10,572 --> 00:41:12,201
- Not now!
- Is there someone inside?

891
00:41:12,341 --> 00:41:13,670
No way.

892
00:41:13,671 --> 00:41:15,101
(Please stop.)

893
00:41:15,471 --> 00:41:16,471
Is there someone inside?

894
00:41:16,472 --> 00:41:18,240
(He walks into the Talk Room.)

895
00:41:18,241 --> 00:41:20,940
For 5 to 10 minutes, we all...

896
00:41:20,941 --> 00:41:22,180
(Ju Hee and Jun Han are still having a chat in the Talk Room.)

897
00:41:22,181 --> 00:41:23,251
We...

898
00:41:24,451 --> 00:41:26,621
(Peeking)

899
00:41:26,981 --> 00:41:30,851
(Flustered)

900
00:41:31,051 --> 00:41:33,861
(Exclaiming)

901
00:41:35,091 --> 00:41:39,200
(He closes the door.)

902
00:41:39,201 --> 00:41:43,070
(Unbelievable timing)

903
00:41:43,071 --> 00:41:45,901
Oh, the dopamine rush is insane!

904
00:41:46,201 --> 00:41:47,601
Oh, my gosh!

905
00:41:48,371 --> 00:41:49,910
I think he knew when he opened it.

906
00:41:49,911 --> 00:41:50,940
He had felt it.

907
00:41:50,941 --> 00:41:52,710
But it wasn't like...

908
00:41:52,711 --> 00:41:54,580
- she was cheating on her.
- Right.

909
00:41:54,581 --> 00:41:56,710
- They're not even dating.
- That's true.

910
00:41:56,711 --> 00:41:59,050
But in that universe, time...

911
00:41:59,051 --> 00:42:00,480
- Right.
- moves faster.

912
00:42:00,481 --> 00:42:01,580
Right.

913
00:42:01,581 --> 00:42:03,021
I wonder what will happen after this.

914
00:42:03,291 --> 00:42:05,251
Maybe he'll go to Jin Wu's room and cry with him.

915
00:42:06,691 --> 00:42:07,891
"What's up, Jin Wu?"

916
00:42:10,761 --> 00:42:13,701
(Yun So sighing)

917
00:42:20,971 --> 00:42:22,001
This is bad.

918
00:42:22,911 --> 00:42:25,511
Was he trying to come inside with someone?

919
00:42:26,411 --> 00:42:28,580
Oh, she's mistaken.

920
00:42:28,581 --> 00:42:30,211
(She starts getting worried about him.)

921
00:42:30,511 --> 00:42:33,081
Then, neither of you is at fault.

922
00:42:33,921 --> 00:42:35,121
But it's not like we're here...

923
00:42:35,621 --> 00:42:37,121
to meet just one person.

924
00:42:37,891 --> 00:42:40,191
- Yes, he's right about that.
- Yes.

925
00:42:42,561 --> 00:42:46,331
(He's so shocked that he returns to his room.)

926
00:42:49,971 --> 00:42:51,131
I can bring them later.

927
00:43:00,981 --> 00:43:07,981
(He's frustrated, and he all he can do is sigh.)

928
00:43:14,621 --> 00:43:16,430
(Then, he thought for a long time.)

929
00:43:16,431 --> 00:43:18,191
Considering how Yun So usually is,

930
00:43:18,231 --> 00:43:20,001
- he must be tormented.
- Yes.

931
00:43:21,361 --> 00:43:22,531
- He must be upset.
- Yes.

932
00:43:26,641 --> 00:43:29,171
(Getting up)

933
00:43:31,311 --> 00:43:34,541
(He jumps up and runs out?)

934
00:43:36,111 --> 00:43:37,111
He's stepping out!

935
00:43:38,381 --> 00:43:41,781
(Where is he headed?)

936
00:43:42,121 --> 00:43:45,560
(To the Talk Room?)

937
00:43:45,561 --> 00:43:48,560
(He's walking...)

938
00:43:48,561 --> 00:43:52,360
(back to the Talk Room.)

939
00:43:52,361 --> 00:43:53,401
Ju Hee.

940
00:43:55,031 --> 00:43:57,101
- Ju Hee, is your chat over?
- Yes.

941
00:44:00,571 --> 00:44:02,101
- Do you have time?
- Yes.

942
00:44:03,571 --> 00:44:05,011
- How was it?
- Bye.

943
00:44:05,581 --> 00:44:06,911
- How was it?
- Good.

944
00:44:08,141 --> 00:44:09,711
- I had something to give you.
- What?

945
00:44:09,981 --> 00:44:12,350
- You don't have any sheet masks.
- Sheet masks? I don't.

946
00:44:12,351 --> 00:44:13,721
You can take some.

947
00:44:14,121 --> 00:44:16,591
I went over to give you some, but I saw you talking.

948
00:44:16,951 --> 00:44:18,190
I couldn't find you.

949
00:44:18,191 --> 00:44:19,760
Oh, you were there to find me.

950
00:44:19,761 --> 00:44:22,021
- I thought you wanted to use it.
- No.

951
00:44:22,531 --> 00:44:25,961
- I was so sad.
- Oh, no. Why?

952
00:44:26,661 --> 00:44:28,900
We're here to find out about various people.

953
00:44:28,901 --> 00:44:29,931
You're right.

954
00:44:32,371 --> 00:44:33,371
I'll wait.

955
00:44:34,701 --> 00:44:36,471
You can come, or you don't have to.

956
00:44:37,511 --> 00:44:39,911
I'm not trying to put pressure on you. I'm being honest.

957
00:44:41,741 --> 00:44:43,711
- Thanks for these.
- I'll see you tomorrow.

958
00:44:44,781 --> 00:44:46,421
- Good night.
- See you tomorrow.

959
00:44:47,151 --> 00:44:48,780
- Bye.
- Bye. See you.

960
00:44:48,781 --> 00:44:49,890
Have a good night.

961
00:44:49,891 --> 00:44:51,890
- You can drop the honorifics.
- Oh, right. Night.

962
00:44:51,891 --> 00:44:53,461
- Night.
- Night.

963
00:44:55,461 --> 00:44:56,760
- Thanks.
- Night.

964
00:44:56,761 --> 00:45:02,161
(What will happen to these two?)

965
00:45:03,571 --> 00:45:04,871
Did you have a proper meal?

966
00:45:04,971 --> 00:45:06,370
You didn't, right?

967
00:45:06,371 --> 00:45:07,441
(Meanwhile, in the common area...)

968
00:45:07,501 --> 00:45:08,970
I'm sure it tastes good.

969
00:45:08,971 --> 00:45:10,440
It'll taste good once it's in my mouth.

970
00:45:10,441 --> 00:45:13,010
Right. It might be different once you try it.

971
00:45:13,011 --> 00:45:14,340
The win-win couple.

972
00:45:14,341 --> 00:45:16,281
I was rooting for these two.

973
00:45:17,711 --> 00:45:21,720
(They had things in common based on their careers,)

974
00:45:21,721 --> 00:45:24,320
- You should be careful.
- I should.

975
00:45:24,321 --> 00:45:25,321
(so they got more intimate fast.)

976
00:45:25,791 --> 00:45:27,121
I have a question.

977
00:45:27,621 --> 00:45:30,490
Why did you ask out Ji Hye...

978
00:45:30,491 --> 00:45:32,231
through the First Impression Vote?

979
00:45:32,901 --> 00:45:34,531
What did you like about her?

980
00:45:34,661 --> 00:45:36,371
The four of them were sitting.

981
00:45:37,401 --> 00:45:40,000
All the other ones were smiling,

982
00:45:40,001 --> 00:45:42,470
but she had put on a straight face.

983
00:45:42,471 --> 00:45:44,710
So, I thought, "What's up with her?"

984
00:45:44,711 --> 00:45:45,781
Did it make you feel competitive?

985
00:45:46,311 --> 00:45:48,881
Yes, it was like a challenge for me.

986
00:45:49,381 --> 00:45:52,650
Like, "Why does she look so tough?"

987
00:45:52,651 --> 00:45:54,020
- So, it was competitiveness.
- "I should give it a try."

988
00:45:54,021 --> 00:45:56,290
Yes, I felt competitive, so I decided to ask her out.

989
00:45:56,291 --> 00:45:57,391
That was my thought process.

990
00:45:58,151 --> 00:46:01,490
Because I had to get to know them one by one, after all.

991
00:46:01,491 --> 00:46:02,930
I had to have a conversation.

992
00:46:02,931 --> 00:46:05,030
So, you went after the one that seemed the hardest to get?

993
00:46:05,031 --> 00:46:06,561
So hard. Yes.

994
00:46:06,731 --> 00:46:09,400
I would have found you tough if you had been there...

995
00:46:09,401 --> 00:46:12,370
because you give off a tough impression at first.

996
00:46:12,371 --> 00:46:13,801
- I look tough?
- Yes.

997
00:46:14,141 --> 00:46:15,710
- You don't seem so easy.
- Really?

998
00:46:15,711 --> 00:46:17,670
You look tough when you're not smiling.

999
00:46:17,671 --> 00:46:18,871
- Very tough.
- I'm tough?

1000
00:46:18,911 --> 00:46:20,440
(Smiling)

1001
00:46:20,441 --> 00:46:21,510
- I see.
- Yes.

1002
00:46:21,511 --> 00:46:22,951
I also tend to get competitive.

1003
00:46:25,151 --> 00:46:27,250
That must be the reason I'm running a business.

1004
00:46:27,251 --> 00:46:28,650
Right. You can't do it unless you're competitive.

1005
00:46:28,651 --> 00:46:30,020
Exactly. People say...

1006
00:46:30,021 --> 00:46:32,091
- that we have crazy eyes.
- Yes.

1007
00:46:32,961 --> 00:46:34,760
- I'm sure we all do.
- Yes.

1008
00:46:34,761 --> 00:46:37,091
- People like us, I mean.
- Yes.

1009
00:46:37,361 --> 00:46:39,131
That's why I was dying to figure you out.

1010
00:46:40,531 --> 00:46:41,731
This is amazing.

1011
00:46:43,501 --> 00:46:45,370
Because we only met here.

1012
00:46:45,371 --> 00:46:47,471
And we only had a short chat over there.

1013
00:46:49,911 --> 00:46:53,410
I saw how you constantly...

1014
00:46:53,411 --> 00:46:55,410
talked to Ji Hye,

1015
00:46:55,411 --> 00:46:58,451
so I thought, "I guess he's going all out."

1016
00:46:58,781 --> 00:47:01,821
I should give everyone at least a day.

1017
00:47:03,121 --> 00:47:05,351
That way, I can get to know them properly.

1018
00:47:06,491 --> 00:47:08,720
(Grinning)

1019
00:47:08,721 --> 00:47:12,160
If we go on dates tomorrow, are you willing...

1020
00:47:12,161 --> 00:47:13,831
to go out with me?

1021
00:47:14,061 --> 00:47:15,800
- I should.
- You should?

1022
00:47:15,801 --> 00:47:17,031
Yes. Let's go on a date.

1023
00:47:18,031 --> 00:47:19,031
What do you say?

1024
00:47:20,041 --> 00:47:23,271
(Jin Young had sent Jun Han her Love QR message.)

1025
00:47:23,541 --> 00:47:24,940
Don't ditch me.

1026
00:47:24,941 --> 00:47:26,010
(But she promises Jeong Won to go out with him.)

1027
00:47:26,011 --> 00:47:27,341
I wonder how this will go.

1028
00:47:28,611 --> 00:47:29,850
(In Jin Wu, Jun Han, and Jeong Won's room)

1029
00:47:29,851 --> 00:47:33,281
Stop putting Jin Wu's footage after happy scenes.

1030
00:47:34,351 --> 00:47:35,951
I'm serious.

1031
00:47:36,521 --> 00:47:37,521
What are you doing here?

1032
00:47:41,021 --> 00:47:42,891
Why? Did you check the result?

1033
00:47:43,761 --> 00:47:45,391
For many reasons.

1034
00:47:46,431 --> 00:47:48,200
I'm here to go for a walk.

1035
00:47:48,201 --> 00:47:49,871
- A walk?
- Well, not exactly a walk.

1036
00:47:50,331 --> 00:47:52,701
I ran here to find someone,

1037
00:47:53,241 --> 00:47:54,601
but that someone isn't here.

1038
00:47:56,341 --> 00:47:57,510
A woman or a man?

1039
00:47:57,511 --> 00:47:59,181
A woman.

1040
00:47:59,881 --> 00:48:01,881
But I can't find her. She disappeared.

1041
00:48:03,081 --> 00:48:05,750
No, I should go back to finding her.

1042
00:48:05,751 --> 00:48:06,751
- Bye.
- Good luck.

1043
00:48:07,681 --> 00:48:09,120
- Can you tell me who it is?
- What?

1044
00:48:09,121 --> 00:48:10,351
Can you tell me who you're looking for?

1045
00:48:11,221 --> 00:48:12,251
