I must win at all costs.

1925
01:24:05,003 --> 01:24:07,803
I want to go on a date with Jeong Won.

1926
01:24:09,473 --> 01:24:10,773
Now that it's come to this,

1927
01:24:12,043 --> 01:24:13,142
