- Right?

2034
01:28:26,863 --> 01:28:28,703
With him in my pocket.

2035
01:28:28,933 --> 01:28:30,032
Cute.

2036
01:28:30,033 --> 01:28:31,203
Right.

2037
01:28:32,133 --> 01:28:35,772
Si Won had a really nice back.

2038
01:28:35,773 --> 01:28:37,413
- Is that so?
- Sorry, I sounded like an oldie.

2039
01:28:37,643 --> 01:28:39,542
- Don't worry about it.
- But his back...

2040
01:28:39,543 --> 01:28:41,882
Earlier, Ji Hye kept saying,

2041
01:28:41,883 --> 01:28:44,382
"Si Won has a nice body."

2042
01:28:44,383 --> 01:28:46,452
- "His toned back is great." - His back was...

2043
01:28:46,453 --> 01:28:48,022
It looked like he's been working out for a while.

2044
01:28:48,023 --> 01:28:49,982
His local muscles are well built.

2045
01:28:49,983 --> 01:28:51,093
- Totally.
- I agree.

2046
01:28:51,223 --> 01:28:53,252
